#

Tuna and Avocado Bowl

10 min
$8.5
450 kcal
Difficulty: 10%
Servings: 2

Allergens:

Fish

Dietary Tags:

High ProteinGluten-FreeLow Carb

Cuisine:

American

Course:

Main

Tags:

Quick MealHealthyLight

Description

A fresh and satisfying bowl combining the richness of avocado and the protein-packed goodness of tuna, perfect for a quick meal.

Ingredients

  • canned tuna (in water): 1 can
  • ripe avocado: 1
  • cooked brown rice: 1 cup
  • cherry tomatoes: 1 cup
  • cucumber: 1/2
  • lime juice: 2 tablespoons
  • salt: to taste
  • black pepper: to taste
  • olive oil: 1 tablespoon
